1. System & Environment
Operating System: Windows 11 Pro (Build 26200)
Node.js Version: v16.20.2
NPM Version: 8.19.4
PostgreSQL Version: 16.x
Default Database Port: 5432
Application Port: 3000
2. Core Backend Dependencies (Server)
Dependency	Version	Purpose
Express	^4.18.2	Web API Framework
PostgreSQL (pg)	^8.11.3	DB Driver
PM2	6.0.14	Production Process Manager
JSONWebToken	^9.0.2	Authentication Security
Bcrypt	^5.1.1	Password Encryption
Multer	^1.4.5-lts.1	Photo Upload Handling
Node-Forge	^1.3.1	SSL Certificate Generation
TypeScript	5.9.3	Language / Compiler
3. Core Frontend Dependencies (Client)
Dependency	Version	Purpose
React	^19.2.0	UI Library
Vite	4.5.2	Build Tool & Dev Server
React-Webcam	^7.2.0	Camera Integration
React Router	^7.1.1	Page Navigation
