Lucide React	^0.294.0	Icon Set
Date-fns	^4.1.0	Date/Time Handling (IST)
4. Infrastructure
Webcam Support: Requires HTTPS (Enforced via node-forge certificates).
Timezone: Hardcoded to Asia/Kolkata (IST) at both DB and Node.js levels.
Deployment: Managed via PM2 on the local server IP 192.168.0.127.
